extends ../../templates/layout.jade

block title
    title #{globals.ipf.title} | Events | Dane

block contents

    mixin secondaryNav(globals.events.nav, "dance")

    .u-container
    
        h1 Inman Park Dance Festival
    
    .Hero.owl-carousel.owl-theme

        
        div
            mixin slideImage('dance-blue-line_l68jcc')
        div
            mixin slideImage('dance-chair_ycmlwo')
        div
            mixin slideImage('dance-y')
        div
            mixin slideImage('dance-ballerinas_hpobmv')


    article.u-container
    
        p This family-friendly performance of high artistic and technical quality includes Q &amp; A with the artists and a cool respite from the bustle of Festival's busy streets. The Inman Park Dance Festival is celebrating 16 years of presenting dance as a part of the Inman Park Festival and Tour of Homes. The Dance Festival's goal is to promote great dance in Atlanta and Georgia. It is the only free admission dance festival that presents both ballet and modern vocabulary in the State.

        ul
            li Atlanta Ballet Center Theatre
            li Ballethnic
            li Emory University Department of Movement Studies
            li Full Radius Dance
            li The Georgia Ballet

        h3 The dance festival takes place on:
        
        p 
            | Saturday, #{globals.ipf.date.saturday.date} and Sunday, #{globals.ipf.date.sunday.date}, #{globals.ipf.date.year} at 4:00 pm and is located at the Trolley Barn at 963 Edgewood Ave NE. 
            = ' '
            a(href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/THE+TROLLEY+BARN/@33.756329,-84.356141,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m2!3m1!1s0x88f503ff905e1bed:0xc1626dc0cd684569") [map it]
            

block scripts
    script.
        $('.owl-carousel').owlCarousel({
            dots: true,
            loop: true,
            autoplay: true,
            responsive: {
                0: {
                    items: 1
                }
            }
        });
